J By: Jeff Pollard August 30, 2007 Whiteboard Friday - Dingo Ate My Whiteboard Whiteboard Friday The author's views are entirely their own (excluding the unlikely event of hypnosis) and may not always reflect the views of Moz. Since Scott had to leave early on Thursday for his extended Labor Day vacation to Idaho, he's entrusted his golden video camera with me to produce this week's Whiteboard Friday. This week Rand sits down with Lucas Ng, who currently lives in Sydney, Australia, and does in house SEO for Fairfax Digital. Rand and Lucas discus the differences between the the SEO market in Australia vs the US, his impressions of the recent SES San Jose conference and his thoughts on the SEO industry in general. Lucas also comments on the SEOmoz blog under the username Shor. So keep an eye out for him! Copied! Back to Top
